description:
Added the bass track, it's quite difficult to hear a lot of the bass in this song, even after boosting it a lot. So the rhythm may be off in some bits but I've used the drums as reference so it ends up fitting quite well.
Meddled around with the guitar a bit too and corrected some notes.
Another note, I think the muted rhythm notes in the beginning are played with guitar in a separate track, but because there isn't any bass during those parts I've assigned that task to the bass.
Anyway, yeah, pretty much done, enjoy!
title: Weevil Bride
